Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.58,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 集 帮我把这个打开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.61,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.59,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经说过了吗 社团集训
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:21.48,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 唔 好像是有… 说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.07,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:28.56,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天不会回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.40,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！让我独守空房？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.55,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:38.30,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊 人家也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:40.14,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 重死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.56,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小祈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.15,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集要抛弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.93,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了 快松手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.20,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去大岛来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:58.55,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:00:59.82,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:05.02,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去看看爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:08.64,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\2c&HDED1DE&\3c&H1C003B&}So everything that makes me whole
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:14.84,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\2c&HD4A0B4&\c&HFDEEFF&\3c&HD37796&}我将无保留地献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:19.79,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\2c&HDED1DE&\3c&H1C003B&}I'm yours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:34.41,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFEFDF5&\3c&HC9C07F&}这世上还是有很多的幸福吧
